[Abilities.Ability_BuildProtoBeam DunDefPlayerAbility_BuilTripWire]
DescriptiveName="质子射线"

[Abilities.Ability_BuildShockBeam DunDefPlayerAbility_BuilTripWire]
DescriptiveName="震撼射线"

[Abilities.Ability_BuildTowerBuffBeam DunDefPlayerAbility_BuilTripWire]
DescriptiveName="防御塔增幅射线"

[Abilities.Ability_ManaCharge DunDefPlayerAbility_ManaCharge]
DescriptiveName="质子充能吐息"

